WEBVTT

01:37.890 --> 01:41.030
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.110 --> 01:43.920
[Episode 24]

01:52.070 --> 01:53.130
It's for your foot.

01:56.000 --> 01:56.800
Thank you.

01:56.830 --> 01:57.880
Let me help.

01:59.789 --> 02:00.680
Lift it up.

02:01.190 --> 02:02.190
[Banquet Hall]

02:01.950 --> 02:02.680
Hold on to me.

02:16.070 --> 02:16.880
Does it hurt?

02:18.480 --> 02:19.280
Bear with it

02:19.380 --> 02:20.470
for a moment.

02:39.800 --> 02:40.600
All done.

02:41.970 --> 02:42.850
Thank you.

02:48.290 --> 02:50.810
[Banquet Hall]

02:49.030 --> 02:52.570
Now, let's welcome Ms. Dianjiangchun!

02:52.640 --> 02:53.900
I need to get in there now.

02:53.900 --> 02:54.810
Okay.

02:55.260 --> 02:58.340
[Banquet Hall]

03:07.500 --> 03:11.570
-Dianjiangchun!
-Dianjiangchun!

03:09.840 --> 03:10.890
[The Amazing Vlog Producer Dianjiangchun]

03:34.920 --> 03:36.010
Turn up the AC.

03:36.030 --> 03:37.060
There are too many people here.

03:37.060 --> 03:38.100
It's really stuffy.

03:38.100 --> 03:39.300
Thank you all

03:39.660 --> 03:40.880
for coming afar

03:40.940 --> 03:42.680
for me and my book,

03:40.980 --> 03:42.370
[Dianjiangchun
New Book Sharing and Signing Event]

03:42.700 --> 03:44.510
"Chun's Daily Taste."

03:44.540 --> 03:45.550
Thank you.

03:51.710 --> 03:52.560
Xu Miyu!

03:53.770 --> 03:54.420
Mr. Duan.

03:55.010 --> 03:56.630
I was wondering
why I couldn't get a helper.

03:56.630 --> 03:58.230
It's quite boisterous here.

03:58.400 --> 04:00.370
Mr. Duan, I'll get you a helper
if you need one.

04:00.370 --> 04:01.090
Well,

04:01.110 --> 04:03.430
five or six people will come meet me soon.

04:03.460 --> 04:04.990
I need you to lead them to me.

04:05.010 --> 04:06.090
Sorry, Mr. Duan.

04:06.120 --> 04:07.680
I'm afraid I'm tied up here.

04:07.700 --> 04:08.930
To make sure the meetup goes well,

04:08.930 --> 04:10.950
how about I ask someone else
to receive them for you?

04:10.950 --> 04:11.660
Xu Miyu,

04:12.030 --> 04:12.960
what do you mean?

04:13.270 --> 04:14.360
Are my friends not worthy

04:14.360 --> 04:16.820
of being received
by you, the lobby manager?

04:17.010 --> 04:18.709
That's not what I mean, Mr. Duan.

04:18.709 --> 04:19.269
I...

04:21.010 --> 04:22.270
May I have

04:22.270 --> 04:24.070
your friends' photos and names?

04:24.890 --> 04:26.350
Ask my assistant for them.

04:32.900 --> 04:33.820
Lu Xiaoyan.

04:36.630 --> 04:38.980
There's a task for you.
It's about the book signing event.

04:38.980 --> 04:39.860
What is it?

04:39.880 --> 04:40.680
I've sent it to you.

04:40.680 --> 04:42.140
Check it out on your phone.

04:44.870 --> 04:46.200
Hello, enjoy your stay.

04:54.580 --> 04:56.240
It's way too blurry, isn't it?

04:56.740 --> 04:57.600
Mr. Ma Wenhui

04:57.600 --> 04:59.240
is an important guest
for the upcoming talk.

04:59.240 --> 05:00.720
It's been a long time
since he last attended a public event.

05:00.720 --> 05:01.510
This is the clearest photo

05:01.510 --> 05:03.370
of his that could be found online.

05:03.680 --> 05:04.160
But don't worry.

05:04.160 --> 05:05.940
He'll come to you when he arrives.

05:05.940 --> 05:08.140
Your task is to bring him to the venue.

05:08.250 --> 05:09.010
Got it.

05:09.200 --> 05:10.740
I obtained some information about him

05:10.740 --> 05:11.560
from the internet.

05:11.560 --> 05:12.310
Why don't I send it to you?

05:12.310 --> 05:13.240
No need.

05:13.660 --> 05:15.090
You should do some research online
as well.

05:15.090 --> 05:17.070
He's a complete stranger to us after all.

05:17.070 --> 05:18.280
Better safe than sorry.

05:18.280 --> 05:19.340
How do I have time for that?

05:19.340 --> 05:20.070
I'm just an usher.

05:20.070 --> 05:22.170
Am I even supposed to memorize
the guest's background?

05:22.170 --> 05:25.070
If you're concerned,
assign the task to someone else.

05:25.070 --> 05:25.910
Hello.

05:26.090 --> 05:27.050
I can see here

05:27.070 --> 05:29.800
that you booked a deluxe king room.
Is it correct?

05:31.560 --> 05:33.690
Why does she have to be so hoity-toity?

05:44.100 --> 05:46.010
Hello, I'm the lobby manager
of Purong Hotel.

05:46.010 --> 05:46.720
This way, please.

05:46.720 --> 05:47.350
Okay.

05:52.640 --> 05:53.640
Have you noticed?

05:54.600 --> 05:55.430
Ms. Xu has rushed

05:55.430 --> 05:57.320
in and out several times today.

05:57.350 --> 05:58.350
Serves her right.

05:58.570 --> 06:00.130
She loves to show off, doesn't she?

06:00.130 --> 06:01.400
Now she can do it all day long.

06:01.400 --> 06:03.460
I just hope she can stay out of my hair.

06:04.700 --> 06:05.580
Next, please!

06:07.000 --> 06:07.560
Hello.

06:07.580 --> 06:08.680
Your ID, please.

06:10.350 --> 06:11.470
Where's my bag?

06:12.600 --> 06:13.610
Next!

06:13.970 --> 06:14.770
Hold on, miss.

06:15.350 --> 06:17.440
I left my bag in the taxi.

06:17.460 --> 06:19.060
All my personal documents are in it.

06:19.060 --> 06:20.420
Could you make an exception?

06:20.420 --> 06:22.400
I'm here for the talk
in the book signing event.

06:22.400 --> 06:23.720
Sorry, sir.

06:24.060 --> 06:26.670
There are over 100 attendees
of this event.

06:26.830 --> 06:28.830
I need to verify your identity.

06:29.340 --> 06:30.900
I advise you to call

06:30.950 --> 06:32.750
the taxi company right now

06:32.750 --> 06:33.750
to retrieve you bag.

06:33.750 --> 06:35.630
You won't be admitted to the venue
without a valid ID.

06:35.630 --> 06:37.720
But the talk is about to start.

06:37.720 --> 06:39.830
Sorry, sir. There's nothing I can do.

06:40.080 --> 06:40.890
Ma'am.

06:47.750 --> 06:49.270
Sir, smoking is prohibited here.

06:49.270 --> 06:51.670
If you are to smoke,
could you step outside?

06:56.510 --> 06:57.310
Cleaning staff,

06:57.310 --> 06:59.310
the reception area needs cleaning.

07:01.450 --> 07:02.870
What am I supposed to do?

07:03.190 --> 07:04.830
Well, this is...

07:06.370 --> 07:08.170
Anything wrong? What happened?

07:08.310 --> 07:10.770
Mr. Ji, we can't reach
the guest speaker now.

07:10.870 --> 07:12.310
Ms. Xu is handling it.

07:13.480 --> 07:14.270
Ms. Xu.

07:14.270 --> 07:14.750
Mr. Ji.

07:15.020 --> 07:16.300
I'll go with you to look for the guest.

07:16.300 --> 07:17.150
Okay.

07:17.170 --> 07:17.970
Ji Feng!

07:20.030 --> 07:20.830
Ji Feng,

07:21.150 --> 07:23.010
the talk will begin in 10 minutes.

07:23.160 --> 07:24.960
Can you stick around and help me?

07:25.550 --> 07:27.690
Mr. Ji, maybe you should stay
and assist Ms. Jiang.

07:27.690 --> 07:29.620
I can go look for the guest on my own.

07:29.830 --> 07:30.690
Are you sure...

07:31.330 --> 07:32.170
you can do it alone?

07:32.170 --> 07:33.090
Yes.

07:33.190 --> 07:35.140
Okay. Call me anytime
if there's a problem.

07:35.140 --> 07:36.090
I'll be off then.

07:38.159 --> 07:38.600
Come with me.

07:38.600 --> 07:39.040
Okay.

07:44.360 --> 07:45.870
Did you receive

07:45.900 --> 07:47.760
a middle-aged man with gray hair?

07:54.390 --> 07:55.190
Lu Xiaoyan,

07:55.210 --> 07:56.340
did you receive him?

07:58.060 --> 07:59.150
Where has he gone?

07:59.990 --> 08:01.790
H-He's gone for a smoke outside.

08:23.910 --> 08:24.510
Hello,

08:24.510 --> 08:26.160
hailing service?

08:28.040 --> 08:30.870
Up next is a discussion.

08:31.120 --> 08:32.840
Let's welcome Ms. Dianjiangchun

08:32.840 --> 08:35.080
with a round of applause!

08:35.110 --> 08:36.820
-Hurray!
-Hurray!

08:39.320 --> 08:40.250
Dianjiangchun!

08:42.630 --> 08:43.539
Dianjiangchun!

08:43.539 --> 08:44.400
[Always on the road
recording the flavors of the mortal world]

08:45.960 --> 08:46.960
Hello, everyone.

08:47.390 --> 08:48.750
Today's talk

08:48.750 --> 08:50.650
was supposed to be held
between me

08:50.690 --> 08:52.530
and my mentor, Mr. Ma Wenhui.

08:52.560 --> 08:54.870
But unfortunately,
due to unexpected circumstances,

08:54.870 --> 08:57.200
Mr. Ma couldn't make it here today.

08:58.020 --> 08:59.100
Nonetheless,

08:59.120 --> 09:01.120
I'm honored to have invited

09:01.150 --> 09:03.030
a good friend of mine to the talk.

09:03.070 --> 09:04.870
He's the general manager of this hotel,

09:04.870 --> 09:07.930
who rose to fame online
for his saxophone performance.

09:11.510 --> 09:13.620
Ji Feng, come up on the stage.

09:14.630 --> 09:17.320
-Nice!
-Great!

09:26.730 --> 09:29.860
First, thank you all
for not turning around and leaving.

09:32.390 --> 09:33.960
Let me briefly introduce myself.

09:33.960 --> 09:36.710
I'm Ji Feng,
the general manager of Purong Hotel.

09:36.740 --> 09:39.100
I believe the essence of today's talk

09:39.120 --> 09:41.480
isn't the topic itself,
but your very presence.

09:41.480 --> 09:43.270
You showing up here is already meaningful.

09:43.270 --> 09:45.150
It's just like a sentence in the book:

09:45.150 --> 09:47.000
"Every meeting is a long-awaited reunion."

09:47.000 --> 09:48.340
I'd like to interview Ms. Dianjiangchun.

09:48.340 --> 09:50.700
Is there a story behind this sentence?

09:52.930 --> 09:56.590
Mr. Ji is fishing for gossip
right after getting on the stage, huh?

10:16.080 --> 10:21.010
[Nanxun Road]

10:21.470 --> 10:22.280
Hello,

10:22.320 --> 10:24.020
hailing service, right?

10:26.210 --> 10:27.210
You found the bag?

10:30.210 --> 10:31.600
Could you have it delivered

10:31.600 --> 10:33.080
to the lobby of Purong Hotel?

10:33.080 --> 10:34.050
I'll be there.

10:37.580 --> 10:40.880
Mr. Ma said he'd like to pick it up
somewhere else?

10:42.120 --> 10:42.920
Okay.

10:42.940 --> 10:44.220
I got it. Thanks.

11:13.020 --> 11:15.560
[Dianjiangchun
New Book Sharing and Signing Event]

11:19.280 --> 11:21.700
May I ask a personal question?

11:21.720 --> 11:23.890
Are the two of you dating?

11:24.710 --> 11:27.080
You two really make a perfect couple!

11:25.890 --> 11:27.350
[Dianjiangchun
New Book Sharing and Signing Event]

11:28.600 --> 11:29.310
Hailin,

11:29.330 --> 11:30.520
I'm terribly sorry.

11:30.540 --> 11:33.060
Mr. Ma won't be back to the hotel.

11:33.130 --> 11:33.800
It's okay.

11:33.830 --> 11:35.680
We already have a guest for the talk.

11:35.680 --> 11:37.600
They're dropping juicy gossip now.

11:37.600 --> 11:39.600
I treasure each and every one of you.

11:39.790 --> 11:40.650
So,

11:41.080 --> 11:42.480
I don't want to lie to you.

11:44.190 --> 11:45.090
The two of us...

11:46.480 --> 11:47.480
used to be in love.

11:57.170 --> 11:57.840
Have you two

11:57.840 --> 12:00.910
considered getting back together?

12:00.910 --> 12:03.570
Yes! Yeah!

12:03.600 --> 12:04.650
To me...

12:05.320 --> 12:07.200
Mr. Ji is a great work partner.

12:07.350 --> 12:10.580
Among all the people
I've collaborated with,

12:10.600 --> 12:13.790
I deem Mr. Ji as
the most trustworthy and compatible one.

12:14.040 --> 12:15.860
As for the future,

12:16.720 --> 12:17.920
I'll leave it to fate.

12:23.440 --> 12:25.460
Just as expected of Dianjiangchun.

12:26.470 --> 12:28.010
Look at the audience's reaction.

12:28.010 --> 12:29.940
These fans have definitely
got their value out of coming here,

12:29.940 --> 12:32.290
as they could witness
something so romantic.

12:32.290 --> 12:34.130
Ms. Xu, look!

12:36.890 --> 12:39.250
Mr. Ji, have you met Ms. Jiang before?

12:39.270 --> 12:40.270
She and I...

12:41.940 --> 12:43.400
went to college together.

13:05.710 --> 13:13.750
[Purong Hotel]

13:13.980 --> 13:14.810
Lu Xiaoyan,

13:15.510 --> 13:16.440
I need you to write

13:16.440 --> 13:18.300
a report about today's incident.

13:18.900 --> 13:20.020
What incident?

13:20.220 --> 13:21.720
What's there to write about?

13:21.720 --> 13:23.330
I demand a detailed explanation.

13:23.330 --> 13:23.970
First,

13:24.000 --> 13:25.080
what was your attitude like

13:25.080 --> 13:26.750
when you received Mr. Ma Wenhui?

13:26.750 --> 13:27.280
Second,

13:27.320 --> 13:28.550
why did he never come back

13:28.550 --> 13:30.080
after going out for a smoke?

13:35.350 --> 13:36.440
I've reported

13:36.440 --> 13:38.460
to Director Bai about what happened.

13:38.460 --> 13:39.960
You can go ask him for more details.

13:39.960 --> 13:41.020
I am asking you now.

13:42.240 --> 13:43.670
How could you drive away a guest

13:43.670 --> 13:45.000
who came to you for help?

13:45.320 --> 13:47.360
I-I didn't drive him away, did I?

13:47.360 --> 13:49.480
I was just following the hotel's protocol.

13:49.480 --> 13:50.720
ID verification

13:50.720 --> 13:51.910
and the no-smoking policy

13:51.910 --> 13:54.120
are clearly stated
in the hotel regulations.

13:54.120 --> 13:55.250
Attitude determines results.

13:55.250 --> 13:56.440
What kind of attitude did you take

13:56.440 --> 13:58.240
when enforcing hotel policies?

13:58.580 --> 13:59.840
The hotel also requires you

13:59.840 --> 14:00.910
to do everything possible

14:00.910 --> 14:02.690
to help guests solve their problems.

14:02.690 --> 14:04.890
Did you help Mr. Ma look for his lost bag?

14:05.710 --> 14:06.860
I was swamped just now.

14:06.860 --> 14:07.480
How was it possible

14:07.480 --> 14:09.200
for me to help a guest
look for a lost item?

14:09.200 --> 14:10.730
Being busy is not an excuse.

14:10.790 --> 14:11.480
Our hotel

14:11.480 --> 14:13.240
accommodates
a large number of guests every day.

14:13.240 --> 14:15.080
You can't treat anyone poorly

14:15.080 --> 14:16.920
just because you're busy.

14:16.950 --> 14:18.510
Today, you made this mistake

14:18.510 --> 14:19.440
exactly because

14:19.440 --> 14:21.620
you didn't take the task I gave you
seriously.

14:21.620 --> 14:22.840
Let me say this to you again:

14:22.840 --> 14:23.840
whether you like it or not,

14:23.840 --> 14:24.790
I am the lobby manager

14:24.790 --> 14:25.960
and your supervisor now,

14:25.960 --> 14:26.720
which means you must

14:26.720 --> 14:28.520
complete the tasks I assign you.

14:31.480 --> 14:32.320
Lastly,

14:32.570 --> 14:34.280
do you know how important

14:34.320 --> 14:36.420
this book signing event is to our hotel?

14:36.420 --> 14:38.360
The entire event could've been ruined

14:38.360 --> 14:39.910
due to a small slip you made.

14:40.030 --> 14:42.230
Could you have borne the consequences?

14:43.240 --> 14:45.200
Isn't the talk going well now?

14:45.200 --> 14:47.860
That's because
someone is fixing your mistake.

14:48.700 --> 14:50.060
Tomorrow morning,

14:50.090 --> 14:52.090
submit a written explanation to me.

14:52.340 --> 14:53.990
Ten points will be deducted
from your performance rating this month.

14:53.990 --> 14:55.150
Take it as a lesson.

14:55.450 --> 14:57.810
What? A 10-point deduction?

14:57.870 --> 14:59.330
I didn't mean to offend him.

14:59.330 --> 15:00.240
I really didn't know

15:00.240 --> 15:02.000
he was the guest speaker.

15:02.000 --> 15:02.950
If I had known,

15:02.980 --> 15:04.840
I would've treated him properly.

15:05.600 --> 15:06.570
Miyu!

15:07.040 --> 15:07.860
That's my sister,

15:07.860 --> 15:09.200
the lobby manager.

15:09.790 --> 15:10.790
Anyway,

15:10.790 --> 15:13.450
you must take responsibility
for your mistake.

15:15.210 --> 15:16.010
Miyao.

15:17.520 --> 15:18.640
It's a real delight

15:18.720 --> 15:20.790
to have gathered with you today

15:20.790 --> 15:22.320
and had such a fantastic talk.

15:22.320 --> 15:23.840
In the days ahead,

15:23.840 --> 15:26.050
no matter how busy or anxious

15:26.070 --> 15:27.280
you may be,

15:27.360 --> 15:28.790
I hope

15:28.790 --> 15:31.120
all of you can find your inner peace

15:31.120 --> 15:33.840
in your stressful everyday lives.

15:34.360 --> 15:37.960
I'd appreciate it if you could continue
supporting me and staying connected

15:37.960 --> 15:38.960
with me.

15:42.840 --> 15:44.120
Thank you, everyone.

15:45.630 --> 15:46.950
Dianjiangchun!

15:46.980 --> 15:48.380
Dianjiangchun!

15:48.400 --> 15:50.000
Dianjiangchun!

15:50.020 --> 15:51.530
Dianjiangchun!

15:55.360 --> 15:56.270
Sorry.

15:56.360 --> 15:58.240
I let out our secret without your consent.

15:58.240 --> 15:59.320
You're not mad at me, are you?

15:59.320 --> 16:00.080
Not at all.

16:00.550 --> 16:02.730
Our hotel has benefited from this event.

16:02.730 --> 16:04.460
For that, I owe you many thanks.

16:04.630 --> 16:06.820
By the way,
are there extra copies of your book?

16:06.820 --> 16:07.700
Why do you ask?

16:09.120 --> 16:11.740
All our staff are your fans now.

16:11.760 --> 16:13.100
I might as well take this chance

16:13.100 --> 16:14.030
to buy 500 copies

16:14.200 --> 16:15.560
for them as staff perks.

16:15.860 --> 16:17.540
What a pleasure for me, Mr. Ji.

16:17.840 --> 16:19.040
The pleasure is ours.

16:20.650 --> 16:22.270
Thank you, Zhichun.

16:22.840 --> 16:23.720
For what?

16:25.130 --> 16:27.460
For being supportive of Purong Hotel.

16:29.570 --> 16:31.300
Nothing gets past you, does it?

16:35.950 --> 16:37.430
How magnificent.

16:39.600 --> 16:40.860
This is really pretty.

16:43.320 --> 16:45.100
What? I won't break it.

16:45.600 --> 16:46.990
There's even a piano!

16:47.030 --> 16:48.040
Get back out.

16:48.910 --> 16:49.810
No entry.

16:49.830 --> 16:52.070
That's a display for everyone, isn't it?

16:52.070 --> 16:52.910
Let's go.

16:53.060 --> 16:53.790
Honestly,

16:53.790 --> 16:55.180
you look quite smart

16:55.210 --> 16:56.840
in this uniform.

16:56.860 --> 16:58.190
Is anyone pursuing you?

16:58.380 --> 16:59.270
Five-star hotel guests

16:58.490 --> 17:02.160
[Purong Hotel]

16:59.290 --> 17:00.950
all have deep pockets, right?

17:00.950 --> 17:03.150
Quickly find a decent one and marry him.

17:06.140 --> 17:06.970
Thanks.

17:09.349 --> 17:10.280
Miyao,

17:10.829 --> 17:11.920
what on earth brings you here?

17:11.920 --> 17:13.369
A certain matter, of course.

17:13.369 --> 17:14.609
Can we eat and talk

17:14.640 --> 17:16.089
somewhere?

17:17.030 --> 17:18.760
How about the executive lounge

17:18.780 --> 17:20.240
you brought Mom and Dad to last time?

17:20.240 --> 17:22.099
Why not treat me to that place too?

17:22.109 --> 17:23.589
I can't go to the HSKP Department
without cause,

17:23.589 --> 17:25.190
since I work in the lobby now.

17:25.480 --> 17:26.270
I'll be off work soon.

17:26.270 --> 17:28.109
Let me get changed
and take you out for a bite, okay?

17:28.109 --> 17:28.920
Out for a bite?

17:28.920 --> 17:30.250
What do you mean by that?

17:30.610 --> 17:32.220
Are you chasing me away
right after I arrived?

17:32.220 --> 17:33.790
Am I embarrassing you or what?

17:33.790 --> 17:34.790
No, that's not it.

17:34.810 --> 17:35.830
Then what's the reason?

17:35.830 --> 17:36.590
Anyway,

17:36.650 --> 17:38.310
I insist on eating here today.

17:38.710 --> 17:39.940
[Purong Hotel]

17:41.210 --> 17:42.190
Hello, sir.

17:42.250 --> 17:43.580
How may I help you?

17:43.620 --> 17:44.710
I booked a room. Thanks.

17:44.710 --> 17:45.910
Please wait a moment.

17:46.510 --> 17:47.440
Today is no good.

17:47.820 --> 17:50.270
There's an important event
in our hotel today.

17:50.270 --> 17:52.050
I promise I'll take you to the lounge
next time you're here.

17:52.050 --> 17:52.960
Next time?

17:53.520 --> 17:55.310
That means I have to wait then, right?

17:55.310 --> 17:56.070
All I have done

17:56.070 --> 17:57.550
is wait, wait, and wait.

17:57.810 --> 18:00.770
When you were divorced
and busy looking for a job,

18:00.800 --> 18:01.720
I kindly spared you

18:01.720 --> 18:02.960
from trouble out of pity.

18:02.960 --> 18:04.800
Are you saying I have to make
an appointment for a chat

18:04.800 --> 18:07.000
now that you've got your life together?

18:07.160 --> 18:08.570
I don't mean any of that.

18:10.320 --> 18:11.560
Just cut the chase.

18:12.700 --> 18:14.180
What do you want this time?

18:14.210 --> 18:16.650
What do you mean, "what I want this time"?

18:17.100 --> 18:18.580
I'm your sister.

18:18.850 --> 18:21.080
It's not like I'm here to rob you.

18:21.390 --> 18:23.340
I'm actually here to beg you.

18:23.360 --> 18:24.980
I'm begging you

18:25.080 --> 18:26.370
to help your nephew,

18:26.400 --> 18:28.610
given that the entire family supported you

18:28.610 --> 18:30.210
through college in the past.

18:30.210 --> 18:30.960
Will you chip in

18:30.960 --> 18:33.450
to pay for
my son's international school tuition?

18:33.450 --> 18:34.140
Sister,

18:34.580 --> 18:36.190
part of my monthly salary

18:36.320 --> 18:38.080
is spent on Mom and Dad's loans.

18:38.370 --> 18:39.630
I'm unable to help you.

18:43.570 --> 18:45.900
You're indeed different now from before.

18:46.070 --> 18:47.060
Xu Miyu,

18:47.590 --> 18:50.510
what a powerful lobby manager you are now.

18:50.540 --> 18:52.780
Since when have you become  so heartless

18:52.800 --> 18:54.110
and cold to your family?

18:54.110 --> 18:56.110
You're living the high life

18:56.110 --> 18:57.640
in a five-star hotel,

18:57.670 --> 19:00.090
yet you won't lend money
to a family member in need.

19:00.090 --> 19:01.780
Don't you have a conscience?

19:07.470 --> 19:08.360
Miyao,

19:09.280 --> 19:10.240
I, Xu Miyu,

19:10.950 --> 19:11.880
can look you,

19:12.810 --> 19:13.550
Dad, Mom,

19:14.030 --> 19:15.030
and everyone else

19:15.170 --> 19:16.860
in the family that raised me in the eye

19:16.860 --> 19:18.720
and say I have a clear conscience.

19:19.440 --> 19:20.200
I've devoted

19:20.200 --> 19:22.200
everything I have to all of you.

19:23.270 --> 19:25.030
The rest of my life belongs to myself.

19:25.030 --> 19:26.890
I hope you'll stop disturbing me!

19:27.090 --> 19:27.850
Besides,

19:28.840 --> 19:30.280
this is where I work.

19:31.000 --> 19:32.600
You'd better be respectful.

19:34.000 --> 19:34.880
Hello, sir.

19:34.900 --> 19:36.200
Here's your key card and passport.

19:36.200 --> 19:36.750
Please keep them safe.

19:36.750 --> 19:37.680
Okay, thanks.

19:38.480 --> 19:39.680
Have a temper now,

19:39.680 --> 19:41.550
don't you?

19:41.850 --> 19:43.090
I need to go now.

19:43.330 --> 19:44.110
You're not going anywhere!

19:44.110 --> 19:44.970
Listen to me...

19:45.200 --> 19:46.350
What do you mean by this?

19:46.350 --> 19:47.530
You're not going anywhere!

19:47.530 --> 19:49.030
Where are you going, Xu Miyu?

19:49.030 --> 19:50.030
I won't let you go!

19:52.000 --> 19:52.790
Xu Miyu!

20:03.190 --> 20:04.190
Excuse me.

20:04.280 --> 20:05.200
I just got off the plane.

20:05.200 --> 20:06.330
I haven't eaten yet.

20:06.400 --> 20:08.180
Would you go to dinner with me?

20:35.960 --> 20:36.680
Excuse me.

20:36.680 --> 20:38.630
Please have my luggage stored. Thanks.

20:38.630 --> 20:39.490
Let's go.

20:45.880 --> 20:46.710
Is

20:46.740 --> 20:47.670
Mr. Tan...

20:48.380 --> 20:49.140
Yes.

20:50.730 --> 20:51.590
But not really.

20:54.850 --> 20:55.890
Who's that guy?

20:55.910 --> 20:57.280
Is he rich?

20:57.310 --> 21:00.020
Do let me know
when Mr. Ma gets his phone back.

21:00.240 --> 21:02.790
I must formally apologize to him
on behalf of the hotel.

21:02.790 --> 21:03.270
Sure.

21:03.270 --> 21:04.350
I'll arrange it for you.

21:04.350 --> 21:04.960
Okay.

21:33.420 --> 21:34.820
Is that Ms. Xu?

21:40.370 --> 21:42.170
I'll walk you to the parking lot.

21:42.540 --> 21:43.300
Let's go.

22:01.010 --> 22:02.330
Is that Ms. Xu?

22:09.250 --> 22:10.120
Ms. Jiang.

22:13.260 --> 22:13.960
Ms. Jiang?

22:15.340 --> 22:16.510
Photos from the talk are out.

22:16.510 --> 22:17.720
Take a look.

22:28.150 --> 22:29.350
Thanks for the hard work, Jiao.

22:29.350 --> 22:31.550
No problem, Ms. Jiang. I just did my job.

23:01.320 --> 23:02.850
Such tasty wine.

23:03.170 --> 23:04.370
Can I have some more?

23:14.170 --> 23:14.930
Thanks.

23:17.730 --> 23:18.660
Mr. Tan,

23:19.000 --> 23:19.830
thank you.

23:20.620 --> 23:21.550
Look what a spread,

23:21.550 --> 23:24.040
accompanied by nice wine
and beautiful views.

23:24.040 --> 23:26.310
It's been a long, long time

23:26.880 --> 23:28.050
since I had so much joy.

23:28.050 --> 23:28.850
Thank you.

23:30.350 --> 23:31.440
Easy with the wine.

23:31.460 --> 23:32.380
Have more food.

23:47.240 --> 23:48.030
Thanks.

23:48.350 --> 23:49.240
Not too much.

23:49.590 --> 23:50.740
Don't worry.

23:51.510 --> 23:53.750
I'm especially happy today.

23:53.880 --> 23:55.490
It took me so long to finally realize

23:55.490 --> 23:56.170
that saying no

23:56.170 --> 23:57.930
feels so liberating.

23:58.740 --> 24:00.350
Today, I said no to my sister.

24:01.150 --> 24:03.150
I also said no to a colleague of mine.

24:03.840 --> 24:06.410
I had such a wonderful day.

24:06.680 --> 24:07.570
Great.

24:07.870 --> 24:09.000
Congratulations

24:09.020 --> 24:11.750
on starting a life free of constraints.

24:12.100 --> 24:12.930
Cheers.

24:25.160 --> 24:25.920
Give it to me.

24:32.240 --> 24:33.480
When I was little,

24:34.150 --> 24:36.250
I listened to my sister on everything.

24:36.250 --> 24:38.210
I hardly dared to contradict her

24:38.540 --> 24:40.540
or go against her.

24:41.020 --> 24:43.260
She was always the first one to enjoy

24:43.280 --> 24:44.740
all the nice stuff at home.

24:45.200 --> 24:47.240
She got the first bite of delicious food.

24:47.240 --> 24:48.960
She got to wear cute outfits first.

24:48.960 --> 24:49.960
I couldn't have any of those

24:49.960 --> 24:51.490
until she got tired of them.

24:51.640 --> 24:53.370
I even had to say thank you to her

24:53.900 --> 24:55.690
and my parents

24:56.640 --> 24:57.570
just because...

24:58.270 --> 24:59.440
I dared not say no

24:59.720 --> 25:00.880
or refuse.

25:01.680 --> 25:02.880
After I grew up,

25:03.170 --> 25:04.500
they asked me for money.

25:05.510 --> 25:06.550
My sister...

25:09.160 --> 25:11.000
asked me to get her husband a job.

25:11.610 --> 25:14.070
Whatever difficulties I was going through,

25:14.110 --> 25:16.110
I would always satisfy her demands.

25:16.870 --> 25:18.120
But today,

25:19.830 --> 25:21.830
when she came and asked me for money,

25:22.680 --> 25:23.820
I said no.

25:24.630 --> 25:25.760
I told her

25:26.370 --> 25:28.370
that the old Xu Miyu who always tried

25:28.550 --> 25:31.150
to please and pander to others
was already dead

25:31.200 --> 25:31.930
and gone.

25:32.920 --> 25:34.890
Now, I'm a free spirit

25:34.920 --> 25:36.650
who's only living for herself.

25:37.290 --> 25:39.450
I wish you could see my sister's face.

25:39.840 --> 25:41.910
S-She was completely stunned.

25:42.790 --> 25:44.510
She went absolutely livid.

25:46.570 --> 25:48.840
But seeing her so angry,

25:49.790 --> 25:51.720
I felt really happy.

25:53.630 --> 25:54.300
Was that...

25:54.460 --> 25:55.630
even right?

25:58.160 --> 25:59.100
Thank you.

26:02.200 --> 26:03.530
You did the right thing.

26:06.150 --> 26:07.120
Trust me.

26:10.810 --> 26:12.530
But are you

26:12.550 --> 26:14.630
genuinely happy now?

26:22.950 --> 26:23.670
Fine.

26:23.830 --> 26:25.110
Let's say

26:25.160 --> 26:26.240
you're genuinely happy now.

26:26.240 --> 26:27.790
You've already said so much.

26:27.790 --> 26:28.790
Why not continue

26:28.820 --> 26:30.970
and pour your heart out to me?

26:31.790 --> 26:33.140
Just think of me as

26:33.350 --> 26:34.240
a canvas,

26:35.030 --> 26:36.690
on which you can doodle as you please.

26:36.690 --> 26:38.660
A canvas can't laugh at you, right?

26:52.210 --> 26:53.010
Right.

26:54.550 --> 26:56.030
A canvas can't laugh at me.

26:58.840 --> 26:59.920
There's actually a painting

26:59.920 --> 27:01.120
I'm longing to paint.

27:01.390 --> 27:02.600
I thought about it

27:02.790 --> 27:03.560
for a long time,

27:03.560 --> 27:04.200
but I-I didn't

27:04.200 --> 27:05.720
know where to begin.

27:06.790 --> 27:09.800
I didn't think I was ready.

27:10.110 --> 27:11.640
I even felt I was not worthy.

27:12.350 --> 27:13.750
There was a moment

27:14.270 --> 27:16.390
when I thought I might be ready.

27:16.530 --> 27:17.590
But then I found out

27:19.760 --> 27:22.220
someone else was drawing
the same painting.

27:23.310 --> 27:25.110
The colors were bright,

27:25.860 --> 27:27.320
and the idea was unique.

27:31.880 --> 27:33.270
That said, every painter's

27:33.270 --> 27:34.960
brushstrokes and emotions

27:35.650 --> 27:36.690
are unique.

27:37.240 --> 27:38.000
Really?

27:41.170 --> 27:43.630
But that's someone else's unfinished work.

27:44.480 --> 27:46.280
I'd hate to disrupt the process.

27:50.000 --> 27:51.660
There are plenty of canvases.

27:53.020 --> 27:56.180
You'll surely find the one
that belongs to you.

27:56.640 --> 27:57.400
Trust me.

27:59.440 --> 28:01.040
Because you deserve better.

28:01.100 --> 28:03.010
♪ Life is full of ♪

28:04.060 --> 28:06.710
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

28:05.240 --> 28:06.110
Mr. Tan,

28:07.300 --> 28:09.420
no one has ever cracked a crab for me.

28:08.240 --> 28:12.090
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

28:09.450 --> 28:10.580
What an honor for me.

28:13.270 --> 28:14.210
It tastes good.

28:13.680 --> 28:15.680
♪ All those confusions ♪

28:14.670 --> 28:15.430
Have more.

28:16.270 --> 28:19.990
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

28:20.870 --> 28:24.870
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

28:28.270 --> 28:30.390
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

28:31.800 --> 28:33.720
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

28:33.800 --> 28:34.880
Take this.

28:35.410 --> 28:36.900
All of it?

28:35.550 --> 28:39.260
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

28:41.070 --> 28:42.870
♪ Busy and restless ♪

28:43.470 --> 28:46.900
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

28:48.240 --> 28:52.300
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

29:03.400 --> 29:04.490
The livestream revenue

29:04.490 --> 29:08.160
has been settled
with Dianjiangchun's company.

29:08.820 --> 29:09.420
By the way,

29:09.480 --> 29:10.680
I've also placed an order

29:10.680 --> 29:11.550
of 500 signed copies

29:11.550 --> 29:12.640
of her book.

29:13.240 --> 29:15.000
The finance department
was very cooperative.

29:15.000 --> 29:16.400
They didn't whine at all,

29:16.480 --> 29:18.280
since we racked in so much money.

29:19.600 --> 29:21.200
As for the lobby incident...

29:24.960 --> 29:26.160
I've looked into it.

29:26.160 --> 29:27.920
It was just someone's family affairs.

29:27.920 --> 29:29.120
What family affairs?

29:29.680 --> 29:31.170
Xu Miyu's sister came to see her.

29:31.170 --> 29:33.300
They had an unpleasant conversation.

29:33.440 --> 29:34.270
The food is quite good today.

29:34.270 --> 29:35.400
What happened then?

29:35.840 --> 29:36.940
What could've happened?

29:36.940 --> 29:39.430
Her sister stopped making a scene
when she saw

29:39.430 --> 29:40.630
Xu Miyu was taken away.

29:40.630 --> 29:41.360
Don't worry.

29:41.380 --> 29:42.650
I've notified the security.

29:42.650 --> 29:43.880
They're aware of that woman now.

29:43.880 --> 29:45.170
She'll be put under control

29:45.170 --> 29:46.200
if she comes again.

29:46.200 --> 29:47.110
I'm not asking about that woman,

29:47.110 --> 29:48.840
but the one that was taken away.

29:50.330 --> 29:51.090
Was she okay?

29:52.110 --> 29:53.040
You mean Xu Miyu?

29:55.270 --> 29:57.480
The girls at the reception told me

29:58.240 --> 30:00.160
that her sister got physical with her.

30:00.160 --> 30:02.880
Luckily, Mr. Tan was there to see it.

30:03.390 --> 30:04.790
What did the security do?

30:04.880 --> 30:06.090
There were so many employees in the lobby.

30:06.090 --> 30:07.150
Did no one help her?

30:07.510 --> 30:09.740
All security guards
were assigned to the banquet hall.

30:09.740 --> 30:11.560
And don't you know
those working in the lobby?

30:11.560 --> 30:14.090
They love nothing more than drama.

30:14.120 --> 30:16.080
None of them like Xu Miyu.

30:16.100 --> 30:17.640
They'd love to see her get humiliated.

30:17.640 --> 30:19.170
She should've turned to me.

30:19.650 --> 30:20.570
You?

30:21.190 --> 30:22.510
What gives you the right to meddle

30:22.510 --> 30:23.910
with her family affairs?

30:24.570 --> 30:26.700
Your position as the general manager?

30:30.400 --> 30:31.730
Feng,

30:31.960 --> 30:33.160
Xu Miyu

30:33.160 --> 30:35.440
was busy from morning till night,

30:35.640 --> 30:36.680
without taking a break.

30:36.680 --> 30:38.030
Then she finally got off work.

30:38.030 --> 30:40.830
Isn't it nice
that someone is keeping her company?

30:45.310 --> 30:47.770
How are the preparations
for the talk coming along?

30:47.770 --> 30:49.350
The wiring is all set in the venue.

30:49.350 --> 30:51.100
The cold buffet is getting ready.

30:51.100 --> 30:52.530
As for the guest speaker,

30:52.620 --> 30:55.450
I'll personally bring him
to the banquet hall.

30:55.480 --> 30:57.940
Mr. Ji,
we can't reach the guest speaker now.

30:57.950 --> 30:59.630
Ms. Xu is handling it.

31:02.640 --> 31:04.770
Alright. Stop restraining yourself.

31:05.750 --> 31:07.810
If you're concerned, go check on her.

31:14.600 --> 31:15.980
♪ A flicker of dim light ♪

31:18.110 --> 31:19.750
♪ A bowl of warm soup ♪

31:20.690 --> 31:23.020
[Xu Miyu]

31:21.970 --> 31:23.880
♪ People in the city ♪

31:24.700 --> 31:27.640
♪ Squeezing into the hustle and bustle ♪

31:29.570 --> 31:31.380
♪ The palms of time ♪

31:30.970 --> 31:37.470
[How are you doing?]

31:33.280 --> 31:36.420
♪ Grinding away the simple days ♪

31:37.030 --> 31:39.370
♪ Sprinkling them into this busy world ♪

31:38.200 --> 31:39.480
How are you doing?

31:40.950 --> 31:42.990
♪ To be tasted, bit by bit ♪

31:45.190 --> 31:47.680
♪ Embracing this radiant world ♪

31:48.260 --> 31:51.290
♪ Keeps the heart from fading to grey ♪

31:51.880 --> 31:55.000
♪ Life's joy, sorrow, cold, and warmth ♪

31:55.730 --> 31:57.970
♪ Intertwined within the mundane ♪

31:59.780 --> 32:02.970
♪ Let us bravely gather up ♪

32:03.640 --> 32:07.010
♪ The forgotten past ♪

32:07.990 --> 32:10.260
♪ There may be regrets ♪

32:11.920 --> 32:14.160
♪ There may be loneliness ♪

32:15.710 --> 32:17.940
[How are you doing?]

32:54.340 --> 32:58.040
[East Changzhi Road] [Changzhi Road]

33:25.660 --> 33:33.850
[East Changzhi Road] [Changzhi Road]

33:41.090 --> 33:42.990
No way.
Did he really carry her up to his room?

33:42.990 --> 33:44.800
Yes, bridal style.

33:45.440 --> 33:46.960
I heard from the girls on that floor

33:46.960 --> 33:48.470
that Miyu was completely wasted.

33:48.470 --> 33:49.660
There was no way to wake her up.

33:49.660 --> 33:52.170
Well, what's the nature
of their relationship then?

33:52.170 --> 33:54.430
In the past, when Mr. Tan stayed
on this floor,

33:54.430 --> 33:56.350
he didn't seem close with Miyu.

33:56.380 --> 33:57.380
Who knows?

33:57.440 --> 33:59.960
Celebrities are good at
keeping their love lives secret.

33:59.960 --> 34:01.400
Just now when Mr. Tan went into his room,

34:01.400 --> 34:02.640
he hung the "Do Not Disturb" sign

34:02.640 --> 34:03.480
immediately.

34:03.500 --> 34:04.700
Juan meant to find an excuse to sneak in

34:04.700 --> 34:07.100
and take a peek,
yet she didn't get a chance.

34:07.680 --> 34:11.340
If Ms. Xu spends the night there,
it means they're a couple, right?

34:23.929 --> 34:25.810
[Camera 01]

34:28.020 --> 34:32.010
[Camera 02]

34:35.570 --> 34:38.739
[Camera 03]

34:39.940 --> 34:46.699
[Camera 03]

35:18.060 --> 35:21.690
♪ Love is truly not easy to obtain ♪

35:25.440 --> 35:29.140
♪ I can't hold on to you
if you want to leave ♪

35:32.630 --> 35:36.540
♪ I tell myself I'm not hurt
once things settle down ♪

35:40.040 --> 35:43.850
♪ But I realize I can’t deceive myself ♪

35:47.430 --> 35:51.330
♪ I always say
life is already hard enough ♪

35:55.070 --> 35:59.100
♪ So what else is there worth trying for ♪

36:02.410 --> 36:06.450
♪ Friends comfort me,
telling me to have a drink ♪

36:10.020 --> 36:13.920
♪ But I’ve already started living
like I’m not myself anymore ♪

36:17.500 --> 36:20.380
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

36:23.740 --> 36:29.590
♪ I feel reluctant to recall
or forget those memories ♪

36:32.080 --> 36:35.310
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

36:38.690 --> 36:44.410
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to anyone
and I can't breathe ♪

36:45.590 --> 36:48.450
♪ I've been indulging myself ♪

37:02.980 --> 37:06.800
♪ I always say
life is already hard enough ♪

37:10.600 --> 37:14.440
♪ So what else is there worth trying for ♪

37:17.720 --> 37:21.870
♪ Friends comfort me,
telling me to have a drink ♪

37:25.270 --> 37:30.070
♪ But I’ve already started living
like I’m not myself anymore ♪

37:32.850 --> 37:36.960
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

37:39.630 --> 37:46.770
♪ I feel reluctant to forgive you
and there's nothing I can do ♪

37:48.210 --> 37:53.400
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

37:54.480 --> 38:00.270
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to anyone
and I can't breathe ♪

38:01.630 --> 38:04.010
♪ I've cut myself some slack ♪

38:31.130 --> 38:32.350
[Ji Feng]

38:32.820 --> 38:36.160
[How are you doing?]

38:36.160 --> 38:36.790
[I]

38:41.240 --> 38:41.800
[I]

38:41.800 --> 38:43.350
[How are you doing?]

38:43.410 --> 38:44.520
[Thanks for the good work]
[I'll come for a look]

39:12.220 --> 39:14.230
[Do Not Disturb]

39:16.320 --> 39:19.930
[Do Not Disturb]

39:21.660 --> 39:22.500
[Cleaning Service Needed]

39:23.110 --> 39:24.550
She's coming out.

39:24.550 --> 39:26.470
Why is she alone?

39:40.550 --> 39:41.670
Good morning, everyone.

39:41.670 --> 39:42.480
Good morning.

39:43.710 --> 39:44.310
Ying,

39:44.330 --> 39:45.800
can you give me the guest complaint

39:45.800 --> 39:46.480
register?

39:46.480 --> 39:46.960
Sure.

39:52.110 --> 39:52.630
Lu Xiaoyan,

39:52.630 --> 39:54.490
when will you submit your report?

39:59.350 --> 40:00.320
Good morning, Director Bai.

40:00.320 --> 40:01.920
Good morning, Director Bai.

40:02.440 --> 40:04.510
Ms. Xu, hurry to Mr. Ji's office now.

40:04.590 --> 40:06.190
I'll handle the guest complaints.

40:06.190 --> 40:09.390
It's time you dealt with the complaint
against yourself.

40:09.440 --> 40:09.960
Okay.

40:11.140 --> 40:11.880
Lu Xiaoyan,

40:12.320 --> 40:13.880
finish your report quickly.

40:13.880 --> 40:15.340
I'll read it when I return.

40:24.110 --> 40:26.040
Did you do what the complaint says?

40:26.220 --> 40:28.800
[A group complaint
about Xu Miyu's improper conduct]

40:28.830 --> 40:31.830
[Lu Xiaoyan, Chen Fangjian,
Shi Huanhuan, Wang Deping]

40:32.920 --> 40:33.480
Yes, I did.

40:33.480 --> 40:34.940
Were you drunk last night?

40:37.240 --> 40:37.910
Yes, I was.

40:37.930 --> 40:40.190
Did you spend the night in a guest's room?

40:40.770 --> 40:41.480
Yes, I did.

40:42.780 --> 40:45.380
So this complaint is completely justified.

40:45.640 --> 40:47.850
I was brought back here
after getting drunk.

40:47.850 --> 40:50.780
I didn't break any rules or regulations
of the hotel.

40:51.050 --> 40:52.890
I wonder what negative impact I've caused.

40:52.890 --> 40:53.950
You're in the wrong

40:54.170 --> 40:55.630
because you're a staff member of the hotel

40:55.630 --> 40:57.350
and Mr. Tan is a guest.

40:58.080 --> 40:58.920
As I said,

40:58.920 --> 41:00.440
that happened during my off hours.

41:00.440 --> 41:02.230
Is the hotel trying to dictate who I can

41:02.230 --> 41:03.760
be friends with after work?

41:03.890 --> 41:04.790
Friends?

41:04.900 --> 41:05.570
Xu Miyu,

41:05.600 --> 41:06.770
how capable of you,

41:06.890 --> 41:08.750
for turning a guest into a friend.

41:09.170 --> 41:11.040
Do you know how others think of you?

41:11.040 --> 41:12.360
They can't wait to see you

41:12.360 --> 41:13.960
be dismissed from the hotel.

41:13.980 --> 41:15.490
I'll earn their recognition.

41:15.490 --> 41:16.450
Recognition?

41:17.480 --> 41:20.010
They've sent me
this joint compliant letter.

41:23.440 --> 41:24.640
I'm certainly able to

41:25.150 --> 41:26.070
suppress it

41:26.590 --> 41:28.750
and keep you in your position
against broad objection.

41:28.750 --> 41:30.080
But why should I do that?

41:30.890 --> 41:31.820
Are you worth it?

41:33.630 --> 41:35.060
You can't blame them for seizing

41:35.060 --> 41:36.410
this opportunity to bring you down

41:36.410 --> 41:38.540
since you invited your own trouble
by mixing work and personal affairs.

41:38.540 --> 41:39.730
I mix work and personal affairs?

41:39.730 --> 41:40.920
Then what about you, Mr. Ji?

41:40.920 --> 41:42.430
Is your relationship

41:42.460 --> 41:44.600
with Jiang Zhichun purely professional?

41:44.600 --> 41:45.920
Aren't there personal interests

41:45.920 --> 41:48.250
involved in your collaboration with her?

41:49.800 --> 41:51.600
You have every right to demote me

41:51.630 --> 41:52.570
or to dismiss me,

41:52.600 --> 41:53.410
Mr. Ji.

41:53.430 --> 41:54.590
But I have to say

41:55.000 --> 41:56.560
I did nothing wrong

41:56.630 --> 41:58.680
and I don't need anyone's protection.

41:58.680 --> 41:59.610
What did you say?

42:02.250 --> 42:02.810
Ji Feng.

42:07.960 --> 42:08.840
Mr. Ji,

42:09.960 --> 42:12.490
-you're needed in the meeting room.
-Not now.

42:12.730 --> 42:13.710
Just come with me.

42:13.710 --> 42:15.440
You'll know when you get there.

42:15.840 --> 42:18.150
Ms. Xu, get back to your work.

42:18.170 --> 42:19.170
You're free to go.

42:20.450 --> 42:21.480
Yes, Mr. Xue.

42:33.150 --> 42:34.510
Tan Jizhou wants to see you.
